@startuml business-hook-sequence
scale 0.8
title Business Hook Points — OAuth2 Session Lifecycle\n(Fresh Login · Refresh Token · Silent SSO · Logout · Session Expire)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor       User
participant "web-gateway"              as WG
participant "Spring AS\n(framework)"   as FW
participant "[Hook 1]\nDeviceAware\nSuccessHandler" as H1 #LightBlue
participant "[Hook 2]\nAuditingOAuth2\nAuthorizationSvc" as H2 #LightBlue
participant "EstablishSession\n/ IssueSession"          as EstSvc
participant "OAuthSession\nRepository"                  as OSSRepo
participant "[Hook 3]\nIdpSession\nListener"            as H3 #LightBlue
participant "EndIdpSession"            as EndSvc
participant "WG Revocation\nClient"    as RevClient
database    "oauth2_db"                as DB
queue       "Outbox → Kafka"           as Kafka
participant "identity-service"         as IdentSvc

' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== 1. Fresh Login ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over H1, H3
  **Hook 1** — DeviceAwareAuthenticationSuccessHandler  (sau password/OIDC auth thành công)
  **Hook 2** — AuditingOAuth2AuthorizationService.save()  (Phase 1.5: code issued | Phase 2: token issued)
  **Hook 3** — IdpSessionDeletedListener / IdpSessionExpiredListener  (IDP session lifecycle)
end note

User -> WG   : truy cập app
WG   -> User : 302 /oauth2/authorize
User -> FW   : GET /oauth2/authorize
FW   -> DB   : INSERT SPRING_SESSION {as-sid-1}
FW   -> User : 200 Login Form + Set-Cookie: OAUTH2_SESSION=as-sid-1

User -> FW   : POST /login {username, password}
FW   -> FW   : UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter → verify credential ✓

FW   -> H1   : onAuthenticationSuccess()
activate H1
note right of H1
  Stores in IDP HTTP session:
    auth_email, auth_device_hash,
    auth_user_agent, auth_accept_language,
    auth_ip_address, auth_provider
end note
H1   -> FW   : super.onAuthenticationSuccess()
deactivate H1

FW   -> DB   : Session fixation: DELETE as-sid-1 / INSERT as-sid-2
FW   -> User : 302 /mfa  (MFA enabled → MfaBridgeController)

User -> FW   : GET /mfa
FW   -> FW   : OneTimeTokenService.generate(email) → ott:{token} = email [TTL 5m]
FW   -> User : 302 /mfa/verify + OTP sent via notification service

User -> FW   : POST /login/ott {token}
FW   -> FW   : OneTimeTokenAuthenticationFilter\n→ GETDEL ott:{token} → username\n→ SecurityContext: {PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY}
FW   -> DB   : Session fixation: DELETE as-sid-2 / INSERT as-sid-3

FW -> H2 : save(authorizationWithCode)\n[Phase 1.5] hasCode && !hasToken && oauthSessionId == null
activate H2
H2   -> OSSRepo : findActiveByIdpSessionAndClient(as-sid-3, "web-gateway")
OSSRepo -> DB   : SELECT oauth_sessions\nWHERE idp_session_id=as-sid-3 AND registered_client_id="web-gateway"
DB      --> OSSRepo : (empty)
OSSRepo --> H2  : Optional.empty()
H2   -> H2   : generate ULID → ossId-NEW\ncopy device signals from HTTP session as-sid-3
H2   -> DB   : delegate.save → INSERT OAuth2Authorization\n{code, ossId-NEW, email, device_hash, as-sid-3, ...}
deactivate H2

FW   -> DB   : UPDATE as-sid-3: store authorize_context
FW   -> User : 302 {redirect_uri}?code=...&state=...

User -> WG   : GET /login/oauth2/code/...?code=...
WG   -> FW   : POST /oauth2/token {code, code_verifier, client_id, client_secret}
FW   -> FW   : verify code + PKCE\nissue access_token (JWT), refresh_token, id_token

FW -> H2 : save(authorizationWithAccessToken)\n[Phase 2] hasToken && email != null
activate H2
H2   -> DB   : delegate.save → UPDATE OAuth2Authorization (add tokens)
H2   -> EstSvc : EstablishSession.handle(\n  ossId-NEW, userId, as-sid-3,\n  newAuthId, clientId, ...)
activate EstSvc
EstSvc -> OSSRepo : findById(ossId-NEW)
OSSRepo --> EstSvc : Optional.empty()
EstSvc -> OSSRepo : findActiveByIdpSessionAndClient(as-sid-3, "web-gateway")
OSSRepo --> EstSvc : Optional.empty()  — no stale SSO session
EstSvc -> EstSvc  : OAuthSession.issue(ossId-NEW) → SessionIssuedEvent
EstSvc -> DB      : INSERT oauth_sessions(ossId-NEW, userId, as-sid-3, newAuthId, ...)
EstSvc -> Kafka   : SessionIssuedEvent → outbox\n{ossId-NEW, userId, as-sid-3, email, deviceHash, ...}
deactivate EstSvc
deactivate H2

FW   -> FW   : JwtTokenCustomizer:\n  oss_id = ossId-NEW, roles, kid → sign JWT
FW   --> WG  : 200 {access_token(oss_id=ossId-NEW), refresh_token, id_token}
WG   -> WG   : Session fixation: DEL wg-sid-1 / CREATE wg-sid-2\nstore OAuth2AuthorizedClient {ossId-NEW}

Kafka -> IdentSvc : SessionIssuedConsumer → RecordLoginSession
IdentSvc -> IdentSvc : Device.register() / recordActivity()\nLoginActivity.recordSuccess(sessionId=ossId-NEW)


' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== 2. Refresh Token ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over WG
  access_token hết hạn
  web-gateway dùng refresh_token
end note

WG -> FW : POST /oauth2/token\n{grant_type=refresh_token, refresh_token=...}
FW -> FW : verify refresh_token\nUPDATE same OAuth2Authorization record (same id)\nissue new access_token value

FW -> H2 : save(authorization)\n[Phase 1.5] ATTR_OAUTH_SESSION_ID != null → SKIP\n[Phase 2] hasToken && email != null → RUN
activate H2
H2   -> DB     : delegate.save → UPDATE OAuth2Authorization (new token values, same id)
H2   -> EstSvc : EstablishSession.handle(ossId-NEW, ..., sameAuthorizationId)
activate EstSvc
EstSvc -> OSSRepo : findById(ossId-NEW)
OSSRepo --> EstSvc : OAuthSession(ossId-NEW, sameAuthorizationId)
EstSvc -> EstSvc  : oldId == newId → return early (no-op)
deactivate EstSvc
note right of EstSvc
  Spring AS không tạo OAuth2Authorization mới khi refresh
  → authorizationId không đổi → early return
  Không có DB write, không có event, không có Kafka message
end note
deactivate H2

FW --> WG : 200 {new access_token(oss_id=ossId-NEW), ...}
WG -> WG  : update OAuth2AuthorizedClient in session


' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== 3. Silent SSO ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over WG
  web-gateway session wg-sid-2 hết hạn,
  nhưng IDP session as-sid-3 vẫn còn hiệu lực
  với {PASSWORD_AUTHORITY, OTT_AUTHORITY}
end note

User -> WG   : GET /protected-resource (no session)
WG   -> User : 302 /oauth2/authorize (Trigger B)
User -> FW   : GET /oauth2/authorize
FW   -> FW   : load as-sid-3 → SecurityContext fully authenticated\n→ không hiện login form / OTT form

FW -> H2 : save(authorizationWithCode)\n[Phase 1.5] hasCode && !hasToken && oauthSessionId == null
activate H2
H2   -> OSSRepo : findActiveByIdpSessionAndClient(as-sid-3, "web-gateway")
OSSRepo -> DB   : SELECT oauth_sessions WHERE idp_session_id=as-sid-3...
DB --> OSSRepo  : OAuthSession(ossId-EXISTING)
OSSRepo --> H2  : Optional[ossId-EXISTING]
H2   -> H2   : reuse ossId-EXISTING  [log: silent SSO detected]
H2   -> DB   : delegate.save → INSERT OAuth2Authorization\n{newCode, ossId-EXISTING, device_attrs (from as-sid-3), ...}
deactivate H2

FW   -> User : 302 {redirect_uri}?code=...
User -> WG   : GET callback?code=...
WG   -> FW   : POST /oauth2/token

FW -> H2 : save(authorizationWithToken)\n[Phase 2] hasToken && email != null
activate H2
H2   -> DB     : delegate.save → UPDATE OAuth2Authorization (add new tokens)
H2   -> EstSvc : EstablishSession.handle(ossId-EXISTING, ..., newAuthorizationId)
activate EstSvc
EstSvc -> OSSRepo : findById(ossId-EXISTING)
OSSRepo --> EstSvc : OAuthSession(ossId-EXISTING, prevAuthorizationId)
EstSvc -> FW      : oauth2AuthorizationService.remove(prevAuth)
FW -> DB          : DELETE prevAuth OAuth2Authorization (old tokens)
EstSvc -> EstSvc  : session.onTokenRotated(newAuthorizationId)
EstSvc -> DB      : UPSERT oauth_sessions SET authorization_id=newAuthorizationId
deactivate EstSvc
note right of EstSvc
  Không publish event
  LoginActivity giữ nguyên (không đóng, không tạo mới)
  oss_id trong JWT = ossId-EXISTING (stable)
end note
deactivate H2

FW   -> FW   : JwtTokenCustomizer: oss_id = ossId-EXISTING
FW   --> WG  : 200 {access_token(oss_id=ossId-EXISTING), ...}
WG   -> WG   : tạo web-gateway session mới wg-sid-3\noss_id mapping vẫn = ossId-EXISTING


' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== 4. Logout ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

WG -> FW : GET /connect/logout\n  ?id_token_hint=...&post_logout_redirect_uri=...
FW -> FW : OidcLogoutAuthenticationProvider\n→ validate id_token_hint, xác định IDP session as-sid-3

FW -> FW : oidcLogoutHandler:\n  SecurityContextLogoutHandler.logout()\n  → session.invalidate() — IDP session as-sid-3

FW -> H3 : SessionDeletedEvent(sessionId=as-sid-3)
activate H3
H3   -> EndSvc : EndIdpSession.handle(as-sid-3, Reason.REVOKED)
activate EndSvc
EndSvc -> OSSRepo : findAllByIdpSessionId(as-sid-3)
OSSRepo --> EndSvc : [OAuthSession(ossId-EXISTING)]
EndSvc -> DB      : DELETE oauth_sessions WHERE id=ossId-EXISTING
EndSvc -> FW      : oauth2AuthorizationService.findById(authorizationId)
FW --> EndSvc     : OAuth2Authorization
EndSvc -> FW      : oauth2AuthorizationService.remove(auth)
FW -> DB          : DELETE OAuth2Authorization
EndSvc -> Kafka   : SessionRevokedEvent → outbox\n{oauthSessionIds=[ossId-EXISTING], userId, as-sid-3}
deactivate EndSvc
H3   -> RevClient : revoke(ossId-EXISTING)
RevClient -> WG   : POST /webgw/internal/sessions/revoke\n  {ossId: ossId-EXISTING}
WG   -> WG        : DEL spring:session:wg-sid-3\nDEL webgw:oauth:ossId-EXISTING
deactivate H3

FW -> FW   : AuthorizationRevokingLogoutSuccessHandler\n→ redirect post_logout_redirect_uri
FW -> User : 302 post_logout_redirect_uri
User -> WG : GET post_logout_redirect_uri

Kafka -> IdentSvc : SessionRevokedConsumer → CloseLoginSession
IdentSvc -> IdentSvc : UPDATE login_activities SET ended_at=now()\nWHERE session_id IN [ossId-EXISTING]


' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== 5. Session Expire ==
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over FW
  Spring Session JDBC background task
  (CleanupOldSessionsTask) phát hiện
  SPRING_SESSION.expiry_time <= now()
  → DELETE IDP session as-sid-3
end note

FW -> H3 : SessionExpiredEvent(sessionId=as-sid-3)
activate H3
H3   -> EndSvc : EndIdpSession.handle(as-sid-3, Reason.EXPIRED)
activate EndSvc
EndSvc -> OSSRepo : findAllByIdpSessionId(as-sid-3)
OSSRepo --> EndSvc : [OAuthSession(ossId-EXISTING)]
EndSvc -> DB      : DELETE oauth_sessions WHERE id=ossId-EXISTING
EndSvc -> FW      : oauth2AuthorizationService.remove(auth)
FW -> DB          : DELETE OAuth2Authorization
EndSvc -> Kafka   : SessionExpiredEvent → outbox\n{oauthSessionIds=[ossId-EXISTING], userId, as-sid-3}
deactivate EndSvc
H3   -> RevClient : revoke(ossId-EXISTING)
RevClient -> WG   : POST /webgw/internal/sessions/revoke\n  {ossId: ossId-EXISTING}
WG   -> WG        : DEL spring:session:wg-sid-3 (nếu chưa expire)\nDEL webgw:oauth:ossId-EXISTING
deactivate H3

Kafka -> IdentSvc : SessionExpiredConsumer → CloseLoginSession
IdentSvc -> IdentSvc : UPDATE login_activities SET ended_at=now()\nWHERE session_id IN [ossId-EXISTING]

@enduml
